  principle: FOCUS_ADAPTIVE orchestrates the dynamic allocation of an agent's cognitive resources by modulating attentional
    weights across vast information landscapes. It ensures that processing effort is disproportionately applied to information
    deemed most relevant to current goals, contextual shifts, or emergent salient cues, thereby optimizing efficiency and
    responsiveness in highly dynamic environments.
