    Let P_t-1 be the prior attentional state/vector.\n\nThen:\n  A_t = W(I_t, C_t, O_t, P_t-1)\n  I_processed = I_t â‹… A_t\n\
    \nWhere:\n  A_t is the attention vector at time t, with weights w_i âˆˆ [0,1].\n  W is the dynamic weighting function, designed\
    \ to maximize(Utility(I_processed, O_t))."
